### Hadith 4:471

*Narrated Anas bin Malik:*

A silken cloak was presented to the Prophet and he used to forbid the
usage of silk (by men). When the people were fascinated by the cloak. he
said, "By Allah in Whose Hands the life of Muhammad is, the
handkerchiefs of Sad bin Mu'adh in Paradise are better than this."

